East River, shoreline, south from East 3rd to Stanton (left) Streets, showing the coal yard of the Houston Coal Co. on Tompkins Street, at the north side of Stanton. In the distant background are visible in silhouette several skyscrapers of the Lower Manhattan area.

June 26, 1936.

P. L. Sperr.
